  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A marathon rally unfolds at the kitchen line, with both teams showcasing incredible patience and control. After a prolonged exchange of dinks, the player in the grey hoodie sees an opening and unleashes a decisive speed-up to win the point.",
    "hype_announcer_charged": "WOAH! We're talking about a KITCHEN WAR! Back and forth they go, dink after dink! But wait! The grey hoodie sees his moment, and BAM! He crushes it for the WIN! What a point!",
    "coaching_breakdown": "This rally highlights the importance of patience and court positioning. Notice how both players are committed to the kitchen line, resetting the ball and waiting for the right opportunity. The winning shot was a well-timed speed-up, exploiting a slight defensive lapse. Players should focus on maintaining this level of control and looking for those attacking windows.",
