    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we witnessed a rather lengthy exchange of the pickleball. It's a game of strategy, and sometimes, you just have to keep hitting the ball until someone makes a mistake. That's just the way it is. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
